// Detune — désaccordage progressif
// Démo : (detune:N) en cents (100 cents = 1 demi-ton)

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:browser
@mm:80

S -> D0 D15 D30 D50 D100 End

D0 -> C3 E3 G3 (wave:sawtooth, vel:80, detune:0)
D15 -> C3 E3 G3 (detune:15)
D30 -> C3 E3 G3 (detune:30)
D50 -> C3 E3 G3 (detune:50)
D100 -> C3 E3 G3 (detune:100)
End -> C3 _ _ (detune:0)
